1
00:00:39,820 --> 00:00:41,280
This wine was just warmed.

2
00:00:41,790 --> 00:00:43,320
Have a cup to warm yourself.

3
00:00:49,110 --> 00:00:51,310
Water chestnut and lily bulb pastries.

4
00:00:55,320 --> 00:00:57,030
With the Yan Army
stationed outside the pass

5
00:00:57,030 --> 00:00:58,830
and the people gripped by panic,

6
00:00:59,240 --> 00:01:01,900
it's rare to find shops
still open on the street.

7
00:01:02,340 --> 00:01:04,800
Lin Mu went out specially
to buy these today.

8
00:01:05,430 --> 00:01:06,760
These bulb pastries...

9
00:01:07,560 --> 00:01:08,280
Yan Xun

10
00:01:09,430 --> 00:01:10,890
used to love them the most.

11
00:01:13,510 --> 00:01:15,039
But that was a long time ago.

12
00:01:17,230 --> 00:01:20,789
During those years when Yan Xun and I
were in the Yingge Courtyard,

13
00:01:20,789 --> 00:01:22,250
we lived in fear every day.

14
00:01:22,830 --> 00:01:25,340
We didn't dare eat any food
that was sent to us.

15
00:01:25,340 --> 00:01:27,420
Only after catching live mice
to test for poison

16
00:01:27,420 --> 00:01:28,950
would we dare eat anything.

17
00:01:30,070 --> 00:01:31,070
During that time,

18
00:01:31,700 --> 00:01:33,250
not a single meal we had

19
00:01:33,430 --> 00:01:34,680
was fresh.

20
00:01:35,160 --> 00:01:37,470
In the height of summer,

21
00:01:38,150 --> 00:01:40,479
the food we ate was already spoiled.

22
00:01:41,000 --> 00:01:41,950
Only Chun'er

23
00:01:42,570 --> 00:01:43,970
still cared about Yan Xun

24
00:01:44,910 --> 00:01:47,640
and would sometimes send over
some good food.

25
00:01:49,710 --> 00:01:50,560
Once,

26
00:01:52,120 --> 00:01:55,220
Yan Xun ate the water chestnut
and lily bulb pastries she had sent

27
00:01:55,220 --> 00:01:56,220
and was poisoned.

28
00:01:56,509 --> 00:01:57,509
I was terrified,

29
00:01:58,430 --> 00:01:59,680
afraid he would die.

30
00:02:00,710 --> 00:02:02,440
I went through so much trouble—

31
00:02:02,920 --> 00:02:03,850
begging for help

32
00:02:04,350 --> 00:02:05,560
and searching for medicine—

33
00:02:05,560 --> 00:02:07,950
before I managed to pull him back
from the brink of death.

34
00:02:07,950 --> 00:02:09,610
To this day, I still don't know

35
00:02:10,000 --> 00:02:11,930
who poisoned Chun'er's pastries.

36
00:02:12,520 --> 00:02:15,050
Chun'er herself
probably never knew either.

37
00:02:15,750 --> 00:02:16,710
After that,

38
00:02:17,590 --> 00:02:19,800
she still kept sending the pastries.

39
00:02:20,310 --> 00:02:22,430
Every time, Yan Xun would pretend
nothing had happened

40
00:02:22,430 --> 00:02:23,760
and devour the pastries

41
00:02:23,840 --> 00:02:25,710
right in front of her.

42
00:02:26,680 --> 00:02:27,840
Only I knew

43
00:02:28,680 --> 00:02:30,630
that the water chestnut
and lily bulb pastries

44
00:02:30,630 --> 00:02:32,030
had long become the thing

45
00:02:32,590 --> 00:02:34,050
he hated most in the world.

46
00:02:42,280 --> 00:02:43,190
From now on,

47
00:02:44,310 --> 00:02:46,240
I won't let Lin Mu buy them anymore.

48
00:02:47,150 --> 00:02:48,000
Zhuge Yue,

49
00:02:49,680 --> 00:02:51,010
you and I are different.

50
00:02:51,270 --> 00:02:53,360
I grew up as a slave in Qingshan Manor.

51
00:02:55,240 --> 00:02:57,750
I don't even know my parents' names.

52
00:02:58,560 --> 00:02:59,310
But you—

53
00:03:00,290 --> 00:03:03,080
you're the noble young master
of the illustrious Zhuge family

54
00:03:03,080 --> 00:03:04,810
and the heir to Qingshan Manor.

55
00:03:05,200 --> 00:03:07,400
There has always been a gulf between us.

56
00:03:08,630 --> 00:03:09,310
Xing,

57
00:03:10,560 --> 00:03:12,490
what exactly are you trying to say?

58
00:03:14,200 --> 00:03:16,060
You don't need to stay here at all.

59
00:03:16,310 --> 00:03:18,110
You should go back to Great Yong,

60
00:03:18,120 --> 00:03:19,250
to the Zhuge family.

61
00:03:19,560 --> 00:03:20,470
Tell them

62
00:03:21,430 --> 00:03:22,829
that you're still alive.

63
00:03:25,840 --> 00:03:27,240
So you're saying all this

64
00:03:28,590 --> 00:03:29,870
just to make me leave?

65
00:03:30,400 --> 00:03:32,000
You shouldn't be doing this—

66
00:03:32,079 --> 00:03:33,740
holding out here alongside me

67
00:03:33,840 --> 00:03:35,590
without even a proper identity.

68
00:03:35,590 --> 00:03:36,430
This isn't the life you should be living.

69
00:03:36,430 --> 00:03:37,290
What about you?

70
00:03:40,210 --> 00:03:43,160
Walk out and surrender to Yan Xun?

71
00:03:44,000 --> 00:03:46,060
You know full well that is his scheme.

72
00:03:56,840 --> 00:03:59,370
The sun and moon cannot shine
at the same time.

73
00:03:59,470 --> 00:04:00,560
The sun and the moon

74
00:04:01,360 --> 00:04:02,310
can never share the same sky

75
00:04:02,310 --> 00:04:03,870
at the same time.

76
00:04:16,230 --> 00:04:18,160
The sun and moon shining together—

77
00:04:18,560 --> 00:04:19,820
I'll take you to see it.

78
00:05:52,390 --> 00:05:57,700
[REBIRTH]

79
00:05:58,150 --> 00:06:00,700
[Episode 21]

80
00:06:23,270 --> 00:06:24,080
Zhuge Yue...

81
00:06:25,900 --> 00:06:26,670
I'm leaving.

82
00:06:28,240 --> 00:06:31,040
You've guarded the pass alongside me
for so many days.

83
00:06:31,040 --> 00:06:33,770
I don't want you to
sacrifice any more for my sake.

84
00:06:35,000 --> 00:06:36,070
When you wake up,

85
00:06:37,070 --> 00:06:38,190
forget about me.

86
00:06:40,430 --> 00:06:43,630
Go back to being the Young Master Zhuge
of Qingshan Manor.

87
00:06:49,070 --> 00:06:51,690
[Urgent military situation. I'm heading
to Great Yong to secure supplies.]

88
00:06:51,690 --> 00:06:54,310
[General Chu is in danger. I'll handle
the provisions. Do not worry. —Zhuge Yue]

89
00:06:55,040 --> 00:06:57,500
The guard
who has been following General Chu

90
00:06:57,600 --> 00:06:59,120
is General Zhuge of Great Yong?

91
00:06:59,120 --> 00:06:59,720
Yes.

92
00:07:00,630 --> 00:07:02,040
So please don't worry, General Li.

93
00:07:02,040 --> 00:07:04,150
Since General Zhuge said he would
borrow provisions from Great Yong,

94
00:07:04,150 --> 00:07:06,610
he will certainly not return empty-handed.

95
00:07:17,440 --> 00:07:18,980
Stop! Stop!

96
00:07:38,409 --> 00:07:39,810
His Majesty has arrived!

97
00:07:52,159 --> 00:07:52,870
Chu,

98
00:07:54,120 --> 00:07:55,000
I knew

99
00:07:56,070 --> 00:07:57,470
you would come back to me.

100
00:07:57,800 --> 00:07:58,390
Come on.

101
00:07:58,950 --> 00:08:00,040
Let me show you the gifts

102
00:08:00,040 --> 00:08:01,360
I've prepared for you.

103
00:08:02,680 --> 00:08:04,340
I've been waiting for this day

104
00:08:05,480 --> 00:08:06,480
for a long time.

105
00:08:19,830 --> 00:08:20,560
Chu,

106
00:08:22,040 --> 00:08:24,040
I prepared this especially for you.

107
00:08:24,680 --> 00:08:26,140
It's your favorite style.

108
00:08:26,630 --> 00:08:27,430
Do you like it?

109
00:08:31,830 --> 00:08:33,510
To make it easier for you
to ride and shoot,

110
00:08:33,510 --> 00:08:35,000
I had it specially altered.

111
00:08:35,000 --> 00:08:35,799
There's more.

112
00:08:36,480 --> 00:08:38,140
These pieces of jewelry here.

113
00:08:38,510 --> 00:08:39,870
According to your preferences,

114
00:08:39,870 --> 00:08:42,840
I had them custom-made to
the standard of the Queen of Great Yan.

115
00:08:42,840 --> 00:08:44,100
If you don't like them,

116
00:08:44,670 --> 00:08:46,120
I'll have them changed immediately

117
00:08:46,120 --> 00:08:48,050
until you find something you like.

118
00:08:54,790 --> 00:08:55,480
Chu,

119
00:08:56,680 --> 00:08:57,560
don't do this.

120
00:09:07,200 --> 00:09:08,860
Degrading yourself like this

121
00:09:08,870 --> 00:09:10,080
won't provoke me.

122
00:09:20,150 --> 00:09:21,550
If you're satisfied now,

123
00:09:22,200 --> 00:09:23,660
please honor your promise

124
00:09:23,790 --> 00:09:25,590
and order your army to withdraw.

125
00:09:26,480 --> 00:09:28,000
The weather is turning cold.

126
00:09:28,000 --> 00:09:29,660
If this stalemate continues,

127
00:09:30,070 --> 00:09:32,510
not only will the Biantang soldiers
not be able to hold on,

128
00:09:32,510 --> 00:09:35,600
but your soldiers may also not endure.

129
00:09:36,240 --> 00:09:36,930
Chu,

130
00:09:37,670 --> 00:09:39,670
I'll keep my promise to you.

131
00:09:40,150 --> 00:09:41,120
Do you remember?

132
00:09:42,000 --> 00:09:42,960
I once told you

133
00:09:43,380 --> 00:09:45,440
that I'd prove to you that I was right.

134
00:09:46,320 --> 00:09:49,200
I'll conquer the world
and lay it at your feet.

135
00:09:49,480 --> 00:09:50,880
I'll withdraw my troops.

136
00:09:51,080 --> 00:09:51,630
Just

137
00:09:52,390 --> 00:09:53,360
not now.

138
00:09:58,750 --> 00:09:59,480
Chu,

139
00:10:00,960 --> 00:10:02,000
just stay here

140
00:10:02,600 --> 00:10:03,800
and wait for me.

141
00:10:08,240 --> 00:10:09,360
Protect the Queen.

142
00:10:09,630 --> 00:10:11,200
If anything happens to her,

143
00:10:11,740 --> 00:10:14,270
neither of you
will return to Great Yan alive.

144
00:10:21,840 --> 00:10:22,700
Your Highness.

145
00:10:43,670 --> 00:10:45,630
Your Majesty is dressed so plainly,

146
00:10:45,630 --> 00:10:48,080
without any jewelry

147
00:10:48,840 --> 00:10:49,750
except for

148
00:10:49,750 --> 00:10:51,610
the hairpin His Majesty gave you.

149
00:10:53,880 --> 00:10:55,610
Your devotion to His Majesty

150
00:10:55,910 --> 00:10:57,550
runs truly deep.

151
00:11:10,750 --> 00:11:12,150
May I remind Your Majesty

152
00:11:12,630 --> 00:11:15,990
that His Majesty had the double cross lock
made especially for you.

153
00:11:15,990 --> 00:11:17,870
Rather than exhausting yourself
trying to unlock it,

154
00:11:17,870 --> 00:11:19,670
you might as well eat something.

155
00:11:20,000 --> 00:11:22,030
The roasted mutton and hawthorn cake

156
00:11:22,030 --> 00:11:24,300
were specially prepared for you
by the camp cooks

157
00:11:24,300 --> 00:11:25,760
at His Majesty's request.

158
00:11:25,960 --> 00:11:27,560
They are all your favorites.

159
00:11:28,420 --> 00:11:30,680
Consort Helian, you're so considerate.

160
00:11:36,200 --> 00:11:37,840
And Your Majesty is a clever woman, too.

161
00:11:37,840 --> 00:11:39,900
You should know that no one could ever

162
00:11:40,390 --> 00:11:42,390
replace you in His Majesty's heart.

163
00:11:42,480 --> 00:11:44,080
Given His Majesty's temperament,

164
00:11:44,080 --> 00:11:45,390
if you refuse to yield,

165
00:11:45,790 --> 00:11:47,520
he will never back down either.

166
00:11:48,960 --> 00:11:50,600
Rather than both of you suffering,

167
00:11:50,600 --> 00:11:52,840
it would be better to accept his feelings.

168
00:11:52,840 --> 00:11:53,900
Come to think of it,

169
00:11:55,480 --> 00:11:56,780
I never had the chance

170
00:11:57,670 --> 00:11:59,600
to thank you for helping me before.

171
00:12:00,720 --> 00:12:02,550
I don't know what you're talking about.

172
00:12:02,550 --> 00:12:04,610
On the way back to Great Yan last time,

173
00:12:05,080 --> 00:12:07,030
if you hadn't pretended to lose your way

174
00:12:07,030 --> 00:12:09,270
and helped General Cheng
draw Yan Xun away,

175
00:12:09,270 --> 00:12:11,120
how could General Cheng have
had the chance to let me go?

176
00:12:11,120 --> 00:12:12,840
I'm only a minor consort.

177
00:12:13,080 --> 00:12:15,140
All I can do is serve His Majesty well.

178
00:12:15,390 --> 00:12:17,550
As for helping General Cheng
draw him away,

179
00:12:17,550 --> 00:12:20,240
I have neither the ability
nor the courage.

180
00:12:20,390 --> 00:12:23,520
Since you were willing to
cooperate with General Cheng,

181
00:12:24,030 --> 00:12:26,750
you surely don't want to see me
remain at Yan Xun's side.

182
00:12:26,750 --> 00:12:28,080
You should be very clear

183
00:12:28,120 --> 00:12:30,630
that Yan Xun's marriage alliance
with your Helian Tribe

184
00:12:30,630 --> 00:12:31,960
was what temporarily stabilized

185
00:12:31,960 --> 00:12:34,390
those fierce and predatory tribes
of Great Yan.

186
00:12:34,390 --> 00:12:36,200
If he takes me back now,

187
00:12:36,750 --> 00:12:38,480
it will certainly cause
a tremendous uproar

188
00:12:38,480 --> 00:12:40,600
among the various tribes of Great Yan

189
00:12:41,000 --> 00:12:42,480
and plunge the state into turmoil.

190
00:12:42,480 --> 00:12:44,140
And when that turmoil begins,

191
00:12:44,710 --> 00:12:46,160
I would wager your tribe

192
00:12:46,510 --> 00:12:48,150
will be the first to suffer.

193
00:12:48,150 --> 00:12:49,120
Enough!

194
00:12:49,630 --> 00:12:51,000
I'm not you,

195
00:12:52,200 --> 00:12:53,750
nor do I command an army.

196
00:12:55,550 --> 00:12:57,680
What happens in Great Yan in the future

197
00:12:58,440 --> 00:13:00,300
is not something I can influence.

198
00:13:05,050 --> 00:13:05,560
[Biantang and Great Yan have been at a standoff
for months. The situation is dire.]

199
00:13:05,560 --> 00:13:05,820
[If Longyin Pass falls, the enemy
will push south. Tangjing will fall,]

200
00:13:05,820 --> 00:13:06,080
[and Great Yong will follow.
This is a case of shared fate.]

201
00:13:06,100 --> 00:13:06,610
[Biantang is prosperous, but we're unprepared
for war and short on supplies.]

202
00:13:06,610 --> 00:13:06,870
[We earnestly request Great Yong's military aid
and a temporary loan of provisions.]

203
00:13:06,870 --> 00:13:07,130
[With your aid, our combined forces
will surely repel Great Yan.]

204
00:13:07,150 --> 00:13:07,620
[After the war, Biantang will repay this kindness
and forge a lasting friendship with Great Yong.]

205
00:13:07,620 --> 00:13:08,100
[For the sake of both nations' people,
please do not refuse.]

206
00:13:10,400 --> 00:13:14,640
The new Emperor of Biantang wants to
borrow troops and provisions from us?

207
00:13:14,960 --> 00:13:17,760
Biantang and Great Yan have been
at war for months.

208
00:13:18,080 --> 00:13:20,540
If you're willing to
lend a helping hand now,

209
00:13:20,870 --> 00:13:23,790
we can surely defeat the Black Eagle Army
of Great Yan in one fell swoop.

210
00:13:23,790 --> 00:13:24,910
Biantang has

211
00:13:25,270 --> 00:13:26,600
always been far more prosperous than us—

212
00:13:26,600 --> 00:13:28,080
and even more so than Great Yan.

213
00:13:28,080 --> 00:13:30,270
Though you were caught off guard
this time,

214
00:13:30,270 --> 00:13:32,670
with some adjustment,
you might still win.

215
00:13:33,150 --> 00:13:34,320
The battle at Meilin Pass

216
00:13:34,320 --> 00:13:35,750
cost us dearly.

217
00:13:36,200 --> 00:13:38,670
Our entire army
has been recuperating ever since.

218
00:13:38,670 --> 00:13:40,910
If I rashly send troops to assist now,

219
00:13:41,670 --> 00:13:43,120
I fear it would only backfire.

220
00:13:43,120 --> 00:13:46,600
Our two states are like lips and teeth—
neither can survive without the other.

221
00:13:46,600 --> 00:13:48,840
If the Black Eagle Army
breaks through Longyin Pass

222
00:13:48,840 --> 00:13:50,900
and sweeps south along the Red River,

223
00:13:50,960 --> 00:13:53,560
Tangjing will be lost,
and Biantang will fall.

224
00:13:54,030 --> 00:13:56,510
When the Black Eagle Army reaches
Zhenhuangcheng,

225
00:13:56,510 --> 00:13:57,750
what you will lose...

226
00:13:59,120 --> 00:14:01,050
will be the lifeline of the empire.

227
00:14:05,480 --> 00:14:06,390
Who are you?

228
00:14:07,270 --> 00:14:10,800
How do you know our country's terrain
like the back of your hand?

229
00:14:15,960 --> 00:14:18,200
I'm an envoy of Biantang.

230
00:14:18,910 --> 00:14:19,950
An envoy?

231
00:14:37,620 --> 00:14:40,070
You remind me of a friend.

232
00:14:40,940 --> 00:14:43,390
I once fought alongside him
on the battlefield.

233
00:14:43,390 --> 00:14:45,120
But he was gone before I was.

234
00:14:45,480 --> 00:14:46,670
I never believed

235
00:14:47,670 --> 00:14:50,070
he was the kind of person
others said he was.

236
00:15:05,000 --> 00:15:07,000
Since he chose to go first,

237
00:15:07,910 --> 00:15:10,570
it must mean
he found something more important.

238
00:15:11,480 --> 00:15:12,440
Your Highness

239
00:15:13,360 --> 00:15:14,590
may as well let him go.

240
00:15:21,510 --> 00:15:23,320
I have 50,000 dans of surplus grain

241
00:15:23,320 --> 00:15:25,250
to tide you over in this emergency.

242
00:15:25,360 --> 00:15:26,620
As for sending troops,

243
00:15:26,720 --> 00:15:29,050
I must first seek His Majesty's approval.

244
00:15:29,070 --> 00:15:30,800
I cannot give you an answer yet.

245
00:15:33,150 --> 00:15:34,610
Thank you, Your Highness.

246
00:15:52,630 --> 00:15:54,360
-Your Majesty.
-Your Majesty.

247
00:16:09,080 --> 00:16:09,840
Chu,

248
00:16:11,720 --> 00:16:12,920
you're so beautiful.

249
00:16:18,900 --> 00:16:19,570
Am I?

250
00:16:26,960 --> 00:16:27,630
Yes.

251
00:16:29,240 --> 00:16:32,240
I've imagined you like this for so long.

252
00:16:32,840 --> 00:16:33,510
Chu,

253
00:16:33,810 --> 00:16:35,240
when we return to Great Yan,

254
00:16:35,240 --> 00:16:36,900
I'll rouge your lips every day

255
00:16:37,030 --> 00:16:38,530
and take you to watch
the four seasons change on the grassland,

256
00:16:38,530 --> 00:16:39,290
okay?

257
00:16:42,710 --> 00:16:44,770
Why wait until we return to Great Yan?

258
00:16:45,000 --> 00:16:47,530
Why not take me outside
for some fresh air now?

259
00:17:00,150 --> 00:17:02,280
You should feel reassured now, right?

260
00:17:13,510 --> 00:17:14,310
Chu,

261
00:17:15,400 --> 00:17:16,839
no matter where you run,

262
00:17:19,480 --> 00:17:20,920
I will find you.

263
00:17:53,880 --> 00:17:54,510
Chu,

264
00:17:55,220 --> 00:17:57,220
every soldier in my Black Eagle Army

265
00:17:57,340 --> 00:17:59,270
is the best of the best.

266
00:17:59,640 --> 00:18:01,600
Dealing with a handful of
feeble Biantang soldiers at once

267
00:18:01,600 --> 00:18:02,530
is nothing to us.

268
00:18:43,850 --> 00:18:44,520
Chu,

269
00:18:45,480 --> 00:18:46,940
we have ample grain stores

270
00:18:47,200 --> 00:18:49,260
with continuous supplies coming in.

271
00:18:49,960 --> 00:18:52,830
Even if we have to fight through
an entire winter against Biantang,

272
00:18:52,830 --> 00:18:54,030
it won't be a problem.

273
00:19:09,590 --> 00:19:10,400
Chu.

274
00:19:12,510 --> 00:19:14,110
I'm so happy today.

275
00:19:15,350 --> 00:19:17,270
If things could always be

276
00:19:17,480 --> 00:19:19,350
like this between us—

277
00:19:20,530 --> 00:19:22,460
no longer at each other's throats—

278
00:19:23,340 --> 00:19:25,210
I wouldn't need this cage

279
00:19:25,510 --> 00:19:26,590
to keep you here.

280
00:19:27,640 --> 00:19:28,510
Really?

281
00:19:28,960 --> 00:19:32,160
My promise to you has never changed.

282
00:19:44,310 --> 00:19:46,310
You want to take me back to Great Yan.

283
00:19:46,350 --> 00:19:48,010
Then what about your consort?

284
00:19:52,070 --> 00:19:52,830
Chu,

285
00:19:53,790 --> 00:19:54,790
in my heart,

286
00:19:56,220 --> 00:19:58,630
there has only ever been you.

287
00:19:59,310 --> 00:20:00,550
If you don't like her,

288
00:20:00,830 --> 00:20:02,310
when we return to Great Yan,

289
00:20:02,310 --> 00:20:03,970
I'll let her leave the palace.

290
00:20:04,160 --> 00:20:06,310
Helian Ling isn't just a consort now.

291
00:20:06,830 --> 00:20:07,830
Behind her

292
00:20:08,000 --> 00:20:10,270
stands the support of the elders
of the various tribes in Great Yan.

293
00:20:10,270 --> 00:20:12,160
If you let her go now,

294
00:20:14,280 --> 00:20:17,280
how do you plan to face those elders?

295
00:20:17,350 --> 00:20:18,830
The Helian Tribe is weak,

296
00:20:19,220 --> 00:20:20,820
and Helian Chuan is useless.

297
00:20:21,260 --> 00:20:23,550
If I hadn't made Helian Ling my consort,

298
00:20:23,880 --> 00:20:25,240
their tribe's pastures

299
00:20:26,480 --> 00:20:29,210
would've been carved up
by other tribes long ago.

300
00:20:53,510 --> 00:20:54,030
Speak.

301
00:20:54,930 --> 00:20:56,260
What do you want me to do?

302
00:20:57,260 --> 00:20:59,120
What do you mean, Consort Helian?

303
00:20:59,680 --> 00:21:02,080
Yesterday, you knew
I was outside the tent,

304
00:21:02,320 --> 00:21:05,000
yet you deliberately tried to
sow discord between His Majesty and me.

305
00:21:05,000 --> 00:21:06,930
Didn't you just want me to help you?

306
00:21:07,900 --> 00:21:08,510
Go ahead.

307
00:23:23,200 --> 00:23:24,860
Go notify Lin Mu and the others

308
00:23:24,960 --> 00:23:26,960
to assemble 50 of the most elite soldiers
from the Xiuli Army

309
00:23:26,960 --> 00:23:27,750
into a squad

310
00:23:28,200 --> 00:23:30,380
and set out with me
at first light tomorrow.

311
00:23:30,380 --> 00:23:30,940
Yes, sir.

312
00:23:35,000 --> 00:23:36,880
[Great Yan's grain convoy will pass through
the forest outside Longyin Pass tomorrow.]

313
00:23:36,880 --> 00:23:38,760
[This is an opportunity.
Bring men and seize the grain immediately.]

314
00:24:05,290 --> 00:24:07,300
Take both the men and the grain!

315
00:24:07,400 --> 00:24:07,790
Yes, sir.

316
00:24:07,790 --> 00:24:08,300
Yes, sir.

317
00:24:08,300 --> 00:24:09,100
-Move.
-Move.

318
00:24:13,960 --> 00:24:14,440
Young Master,

319
00:24:14,440 --> 00:24:15,510
there's something wrong with the grain.

320
00:24:15,510 --> 00:24:16,310
It's all sand!

321
00:24:22,120 --> 00:24:24,350
When I brought food to Her Majesty today,

322
00:24:24,350 --> 00:24:27,000
I unexpectedly caught her
trying to use this hairpin

323
00:24:27,000 --> 00:24:28,800
to pick the lock on the iron cage.

324
00:24:29,720 --> 00:24:32,660
Not only did she disregard
Your Majesty's affection for her,

325
00:24:32,660 --> 00:24:34,590
but she even tried to manipulate me

326
00:24:34,600 --> 00:24:36,630
into helping her escape.

327
00:24:37,220 --> 00:24:38,950
Since she wants you to help her,

328
00:24:39,990 --> 00:24:40,920
why don't you...

329
00:24:43,310 --> 00:24:44,630
help her then?

330
00:24:49,550 --> 00:24:51,270
Oh no, it's a trap!

331
00:25:01,330 --> 00:25:01,890
Retreat!

332
00:25:04,160 --> 00:25:04,720
Retreat!

333
00:25:09,360 --> 00:25:10,160
Young Master,

334
00:25:10,290 --> 00:25:11,280
I'll lead some men to distract them.

335
00:25:11,280 --> 00:25:12,080
Alright, go.

336
00:25:16,400 --> 00:25:16,960
Stop!

337
00:25:18,110 --> 00:25:18,670
This way!

338
00:25:21,810 --> 00:25:22,470
After them!

339
00:25:23,130 --> 00:25:23,650
Hurry!

340
00:25:28,730 --> 00:25:29,830
It's a cliff down here.

341
00:25:29,830 --> 00:25:31,460
Fall off that,
and you're dead or crippled.

342
00:25:31,460 --> 00:25:32,220
Let's go!

343
00:25:32,700 --> 00:25:33,500
Go!

344
00:25:43,790 --> 00:25:46,070
We've been at a stalemate
with the Biantang army for days,

345
00:25:46,070 --> 00:25:48,160
and they have been behind their walls.

346
00:25:48,160 --> 00:25:48,750
Now,

347
00:25:49,270 --> 00:25:51,400
General Chu Qiao of Biantang's Xiuli Army

348
00:25:51,400 --> 00:25:52,800
is in my camp in Great Yan,

349
00:25:52,920 --> 00:25:55,980
and the main force of the Xiuli Army
was ambushed today.

350
00:25:57,030 --> 00:25:58,830
Longyin Pass is now leaderless.

351
00:25:59,310 --> 00:26:00,640
We will depart tonight,

352
00:26:01,160 --> 00:26:02,360
press our advantage,

353
00:26:02,680 --> 00:26:04,130
and take Longyin Pass in one fell swoop!

354
00:26:04,130 --> 00:26:05,760
Yes, Your Majesty!

355
00:26:33,270 --> 00:26:33,920
Stop!

356
00:26:36,960 --> 00:26:37,760
Your Majesty,

357
00:26:37,960 --> 00:26:38,790
it's already broad daylight.

358
00:26:38,790 --> 00:26:39,630
The scouts report

359
00:26:39,630 --> 00:26:41,270
that the gates of Longyin Pass
are still tightly shut

360
00:26:41,270 --> 00:26:42,600
with no signs of activity.

361
00:26:42,600 --> 00:26:44,190
Logically, Biantang's sentries

362
00:26:44,190 --> 00:26:46,110
should've already learned
that we've mobilized.

363
00:26:46,110 --> 00:26:46,790
I'm just worried...

364
00:26:46,790 --> 00:26:47,480
Pass on my orders—

365
00:26:47,480 --> 00:26:49,480
full army advances swiftly
through the valley

366
00:26:49,480 --> 00:26:50,550
and strikes the pass directly!

367
00:26:50,550 --> 00:26:51,350
Your Majesty.

368
00:26:53,000 --> 00:26:53,480
March!

369
00:26:53,480 --> 00:26:54,030
Hurry!

370
00:27:06,140 --> 00:27:06,940
Your Majesty,

371
00:27:07,000 --> 00:27:08,250
the terrain ahead is treacherous.

372
00:27:08,250 --> 00:27:09,510
Why don't I go first...

373
00:27:12,310 --> 00:27:13,070
Ambush!

374
00:27:17,940 --> 00:27:18,440
Fire!

375
00:28:08,540 --> 00:28:09,980
Zhuge Yue.

376
00:28:10,760 --> 00:28:12,020
This letter is forged.

377
00:28:12,790 --> 00:28:15,330
It doesn't have the secret code
of Qingshan Manor on it.

378
00:28:15,330 --> 00:28:18,000
This lantern came from the direction
of the Great Yan military camp.

379
00:28:18,000 --> 00:28:18,880
Only General Chu

380
00:28:18,880 --> 00:28:20,590
knows our method of messaging
at Qingshan Manor.

381
00:28:20,590 --> 00:28:21,240
Then why would she

382
00:28:21,240 --> 00:28:22,790
send us a false message?

383
00:28:23,030 --> 00:28:23,830
Notify Lin Mu

384
00:28:24,080 --> 00:28:25,680
to assemble the elites of the Xiuli Army

385
00:28:25,680 --> 00:28:27,160
and set out immediately tonight.

386
00:28:27,160 --> 00:28:27,720
Yes, sir.

387
00:28:28,360 --> 00:28:28,950
Wait.

388
00:28:29,830 --> 00:28:30,780
And tell He Xiao

389
00:28:30,830 --> 00:28:32,090
to set out immediately

390
00:28:32,240 --> 00:28:33,640
to 50 li outside Longyin Pass

391
00:28:33,640 --> 00:28:35,640
to meet Zhao Che's reinforcements.

392
00:29:42,440 --> 00:29:43,170
General Chu?

393
00:29:47,750 --> 00:29:48,480
General Chu?

394
00:29:54,510 --> 00:29:55,240
General Chu?

395
00:29:55,750 --> 00:29:56,610
Someone, come!

396
00:29:58,540 --> 00:30:00,240
-Your Highness.
-Your Highness!

397
00:30:00,240 --> 00:30:01,240
Open the door.

398
00:30:03,440 --> 00:30:04,240
Open the door!

399
00:30:14,830 --> 00:30:15,880
Be careful.

400
00:30:22,160 --> 00:30:23,960
Catch her! Don't let her escape!

401
00:30:28,330 --> 00:30:29,200
Catch her!

402
00:30:34,570 --> 00:30:35,770
Don't let her escape!

403
00:30:52,240 --> 00:30:52,960
Stop!

404
00:31:12,640 --> 00:31:14,310
Help! Fire!

405
00:31:24,510 --> 00:31:25,710
Hurry! Keep chasing!

406
00:31:26,270 --> 00:31:27,760
Go back and put out the fire!

407
00:31:27,760 --> 00:31:29,020
The granary is on fire!

408
00:31:29,160 --> 00:31:30,070
Get water!

409
00:31:30,470 --> 00:31:30,990
Quick!

410
00:32:20,320 --> 00:32:21,120
Your Majesty.

411
00:33:02,790 --> 00:33:05,000
♪ The flowers fall into the sleeves ♪

412
00:33:05,110 --> 00:33:07,660
♪ They do not understand my sorrow ♪

413
00:33:08,090 --> 00:33:09,390
♪ With a pot of wine ♪

414
00:33:09,420 --> 00:33:10,880
♪ My longing surges ♪

415
00:33:10,900 --> 00:33:13,410
♪ I become haggard ♪

416
00:33:14,020 --> 00:33:16,460
♪ Soft rain patters on the windowpane ♪

417
00:33:16,510 --> 00:33:19,330
♪ Awakening from the dream,
I no longer know what year it is ♪

418
00:33:19,350 --> 00:33:21,050
♪ My love remains ♪

419
00:33:21,360 --> 00:33:24,730
♪ But you're already gone ♪

420
00:33:24,760 --> 00:33:27,030
♪ What I seek in life ♪

421
00:33:27,050 --> 00:33:28,640
♪ Is nothing more
than to look back once more ♪

422
00:33:28,660 --> 00:33:31,250
♪ With the fragrance still lingering ♪

423
00:33:31,270 --> 00:33:32,860
♪ In these trembling hands ♪

424
00:33:32,880 --> 00:33:36,070
♪ My longing still rests ♪

425
00:33:36,090 --> 00:33:38,450
♪ Words left unspoken ♪

426
00:33:38,030 --> 00:33:38,750
Zhuge Yue,

427
00:33:38,480 --> 00:33:39,990
♪ Turn into guilt ♪

428
00:33:39,590 --> 00:33:40,400
you've beaten me again.

429
00:33:40,010 --> 00:33:42,650
♪ Beneath the stars ♪

430
00:33:42,690 --> 00:33:47,550
♪ Rippling throughout this life ♪

431
00:33:43,310 --> 00:33:44,510
I beat you every time.

432
00:33:45,230 --> 00:33:46,830
Why do you never get mad at me?

433
00:33:47,580 --> 00:33:48,970
♪ I ask the vast sky ♪

434
00:33:49,000 --> 00:33:51,250
♪ The wind is light,
but my longing is heavy ♪

435
00:33:51,270 --> 00:33:53,720
♪ How do we start over? ♪

436
00:33:52,720 --> 00:33:54,240
Keep your hands to yourself.

437
00:33:53,740 --> 00:33:57,050
♪ How do we love
and hold on without parting ♪

438
00:33:57,080 --> 00:33:59,330
♪ Or misunderstanding each other? ♪

439
00:33:59,360 --> 00:34:02,770
♪ Do not let me only understand
the meaning of a fleeting glance ♪

440
00:34:02,110 --> 00:34:02,960
Because...

441
00:34:02,790 --> 00:34:05,110
♪ When my eyes are red with tears ♪

442
00:34:04,790 --> 00:34:06,160
you're my only friend.

443
00:34:05,130 --> 00:34:08,010
♪ What cannot be kept,
can only be sent away ♪

444
00:34:06,720 --> 00:34:08,480
We will never truly
stand on opposing sides.

445
00:34:08,040 --> 00:34:11,300
♪ In the end ♪

446
00:34:41,250 --> 00:34:42,050
Your Majesty,

447
00:34:42,320 --> 00:34:43,179
let's retreat.

448
00:34:43,590 --> 00:34:45,190
It'll be too late if we don't!

449
00:34:46,880 --> 00:34:47,810
Pass on my order:

450
00:34:48,440 --> 00:34:50,100
full army withdraws by the same route!

451
00:34:50,100 --> 00:34:51,159
His Majesty orders

452
00:34:51,230 --> 00:34:53,030
a full retreat by the same route!

453
00:35:01,230 --> 00:35:02,030
Your Majesty!

454
00:35:02,530 --> 00:35:03,250
Your Majesty,

455
00:35:03,250 --> 00:35:05,480
Li Qi has led the Biantang Army
to block our retreat from behind.

456
00:35:05,480 --> 00:35:06,850
Our main camp has also been set on fire!

457
00:35:06,850 --> 00:35:07,780
We can't go back!

458
00:35:08,110 --> 00:35:08,910
Your Majesty,

459
00:35:09,150 --> 00:35:11,000
let the remaining Black Eagle Army
hold off Zhuge Yue

460
00:35:11,000 --> 00:35:12,800
while you immediately retreat
through Rongguan Path

461
00:35:12,800 --> 00:35:13,320
and return to Great Yan!

462
00:35:13,320 --> 00:35:13,880
No!

463
00:35:15,270 --> 00:35:16,950
I can't leave the Black Eagle Army behind.

464
00:35:16,950 --> 00:35:18,550
I brought them here.

465
00:35:18,630 --> 00:35:19,480
As long as we live,

466
00:35:19,480 --> 00:35:20,590
we can fight another day!

467
00:35:20,590 --> 00:35:21,880
If anything happens to Your Majesty,

468
00:35:21,880 --> 00:35:24,280
Great Yan will have no chance
to rise again!

469
00:35:25,670 --> 00:35:28,550
Please return to Great Yan at once,
Your Majesty!

470
00:35:31,060 --> 00:35:33,190
Let's retreat through Rongguan Path.

471
00:35:33,240 --> 00:35:33,990
Guys,

472
00:35:34,190 --> 00:35:35,720
follow me to cover the rear!

473
00:35:38,830 --> 00:35:39,390
Go!

474
00:35:49,660 --> 00:35:50,460
Young Master,

475
00:35:50,670 --> 00:35:51,930
Yan Xun didn't return.

476
00:35:52,190 --> 00:35:54,880
He led a small group of men
and ran toward the valley.

477
00:35:54,880 --> 00:35:56,880
Li Qi's troops have cut off his rear.

478
00:35:57,240 --> 00:35:58,840
He won't walk into that trap.

479
00:35:58,880 --> 00:36:00,550
His only option is to stake everything

480
00:36:00,550 --> 00:36:01,960
and take Rongguan Path instead.

481
00:36:01,960 --> 00:36:02,820
Rongguan Path?

482
00:36:03,410 --> 00:36:04,820
Isn't that an abandoned route?

483
00:36:04,820 --> 00:36:05,840
It's full of swamps and lakes.

484
00:36:05,840 --> 00:36:07,570
One wrong step and you're dead.

485
00:36:07,710 --> 00:36:09,460
The terrain of Rongguan Path
is treacherous.

486
00:36:09,460 --> 00:36:11,070
Not only is fleeing through it dangerous,

487
00:36:11,070 --> 00:36:14,000
but pursuing them
will also be extremely difficult.

488
00:36:14,030 --> 00:36:15,360
Given Yan Xun's nature,

489
00:36:16,280 --> 00:36:18,050
he will certainly
take this desperate gamble.

490
00:36:18,050 --> 00:36:18,850
Young Master,

491
00:36:18,880 --> 00:36:20,150
we can't let them escape.

492
00:36:20,150 --> 00:36:21,750
Let's pursue them right now.

493
00:36:56,080 --> 00:36:57,610
Your Majesty, you go first.

494
00:36:57,710 --> 00:36:58,840
I'll cover the rear.

495
00:37:03,590 --> 00:37:04,800
I'll go intercept Yan Xun.

496
00:37:04,800 --> 00:37:05,880
You guys split up!

497
00:37:17,800 --> 00:37:18,400
Kill them!

498
00:37:47,800 --> 00:37:48,470
Chu,

499
00:37:48,960 --> 00:37:50,370
now that things have come to this,

500
00:37:50,370 --> 00:37:53,440
dying at your hands
would be no great regret.

501
00:37:53,920 --> 00:37:55,230
If you want to kill me,

502
00:37:56,230 --> 00:37:57,400
then come and do it.

503
00:38:25,370 --> 00:38:27,540
[Yan Shicheng]

504
00:38:38,880 --> 00:38:39,610
How do you...

505
00:38:41,440 --> 00:38:42,640
How do you have these?

506
00:38:42,790 --> 00:38:44,240
After what happened at Jiuyou Platform,

507
00:38:44,240 --> 00:38:48,220
♪ The sky is so vast ♪

508
00:38:45,280 --> 00:38:46,400
I asked Zhao Song

509
00:38:47,840 --> 00:38:50,190
to help me collect them
from their bodies, one by one.

510
00:38:48,240 --> 00:38:50,730
♪ The dark clouds are gray ♪

511
00:38:50,840 --> 00:38:52,100
Originally, I thought

512
00:38:52,550 --> 00:38:53,800
that one day

513
00:38:53,120 --> 00:38:56,880
♪ The rain is falling ♪

514
00:38:54,190 --> 00:38:56,440
you and I would avenge them together.

515
00:38:56,900 --> 00:39:00,260
♪ The eagle is flying ♪

516
00:38:58,690 --> 00:39:01,880
Once you had made peace with
what happened at Jiuyou Platform,

517
00:39:01,880 --> 00:39:03,710
I would give them to you properly.

518
00:39:02,310 --> 00:39:06,100
♪ In the vast wilderness ♪

519
00:39:04,840 --> 00:39:05,840
But now,

520
00:39:06,120 --> 00:39:09,590
♪ The wind blows ♪

521
00:39:07,520 --> 00:39:09,920
maybe there'll never be that chance again.

522
00:39:11,020 --> 00:39:11,750
Yan Xun,

523
00:39:11,620 --> 00:39:14,690
♪ I'm fearless of death ♪

524
00:39:12,980 --> 00:39:14,270
think of your family.

525
00:39:14,920 --> 00:39:18,440
♪ And I'll never have regrets ♪

526
00:39:15,020 --> 00:39:16,510
Think about your father.

527
00:39:17,670 --> 00:39:20,820
He was loyal and devoted to his people
and his country all his life.

528
00:39:20,770 --> 00:39:28,290
♪ The lonely black eagle ♪

529
00:39:21,670 --> 00:39:24,470
Now, the people of Great Yan
are living in misery.

530
00:39:25,040 --> 00:39:26,570
Is this the Great Yan

531
00:39:26,970 --> 00:39:28,460
you want him to see?

532
00:39:29,070 --> 00:39:30,780
Do you want to live in hatred forever?

533
00:39:29,540 --> 00:39:32,910
♪ Is flying against the light ♪

534
00:39:32,480 --> 00:39:33,920
I'll give you two choices.

535
00:39:33,720 --> 00:39:36,920
♪ Where is my hometown? ♪

536
00:39:35,790 --> 00:39:36,400
Either

537
00:39:37,440 --> 00:39:39,520
we fight to the death here today—

538
00:39:37,460 --> 00:39:46,420
♪ In the vast world ♪

539
00:39:39,920 --> 00:39:40,880
only one of us

540
00:39:40,880 --> 00:39:42,480
walks out alive—

541
00:39:44,670 --> 00:39:45,610
or...

542
00:39:46,440 --> 00:39:49,850
♪ I have no origin ♪

543
00:39:48,000 --> 00:39:49,200
for the next 10 years,

544
00:39:49,480 --> 00:39:51,920
you are not to set foot in Biantang again!

545
00:39:50,500 --> 00:39:54,100
♪ And no destination ♪

546
00:39:54,670 --> 00:40:02,720
♪ A pair of stubborn wings ♪

547
00:40:02,840 --> 00:40:11,120
♪ Is born to fly ♪

548
00:40:13,020 --> 00:40:14,220
For the next 10 years,

549
00:40:14,980 --> 00:40:16,230
Great Yan will not

550
00:40:17,260 --> 00:40:19,030
step into Biantang again.

551
00:40:26,200 --> 00:40:27,000
Your Majesty.

552
00:40:50,410 --> 00:40:51,280
Yan Xun...

553
00:40:52,820 --> 00:40:53,820
How I wish

554
00:40:54,870 --> 00:40:57,270
things could've ended differently for us.

555
00:41:20,360 --> 00:41:21,110
Your Highness,

556
00:41:21,110 --> 00:41:22,630
the time is ripe now.

557
00:41:22,660 --> 00:41:24,100
We must act immediately!

558
00:41:25,050 --> 00:41:27,020
The guilty official Sun Di
has stolen the military tally!

559
00:41:27,020 --> 00:41:28,020
It's utter treason!

560
00:41:28,020 --> 00:41:29,370
Seize him at once!

561
00:41:30,540 --> 00:41:31,170
Mother,

562
00:41:31,190 --> 00:41:32,520
you would surely

563
00:41:32,650 --> 00:41:33,770
be proud of me.

564
00:41:33,940 --> 00:41:34,580
We can

565
00:41:34,690 --> 00:41:36,170
finally put all of this behind us.

566
00:41:36,170 --> 00:41:37,700
Why couldn't you let him go?

567
00:41:37,810 --> 00:41:38,660
Li Ce

568
00:41:38,690 --> 00:41:40,890
was never worthy of the dragon robe
from the day he was born!

